description: To give you the always-much-needed boost, this cool truck is taking Acai berries, the ever-delicious and nutritious superfood, and offering a delectable variety of healthy smoothies & bowls. The bowls all begin with Acai & Guarana, and the offerings include...Over The Rainbow- blend of banana & apple juice, topped with blueberry, banana, and premium organic granola- the perfectly sweet light treatPoseidon’s Trident- blend of almond milk, PB2, Banana, topped with blueberry and premium organic granola- the perfectly powerful treatCookie Monster- blend of banana and coconut water, topped with Nutella and premium organic granola- the perfectly naughty treatThis entire guilt-free selection of nutrient-rich fruity treats will send you straight to tropical bliss.You can always find Acai Hut in The Infinite Monkey Theorem Winery lot at 121 Pickle Rd Ste 110, Austin TX 78704. Come out soon and take a tasty trip to paradise!
name: Acai Hut
